Package: rbrsa
Title: Fetch Turkish Banking Sector Data from BRSA (BDDK)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Ozan",    family = "Bakis",
    email = "ozanbakis@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    An R package for automated access to Turkish banking sector data from the Turkish Banking Regulation 
    and Supervision Agency (BRSA, known as BDDK in Turkish). 
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/obakis/rbrsa, https://obakis.github.io/rbrsa
BugReports: https://github.com/obakis/rbrsa/issues
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    httr2 (>= 1.0.0),
    jsonlite (>= 1.8.0),
    writexl 
Suggests:
    dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    scales,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
